<br>
RRS has been doing experimental rocketry for 60 years and has a perfect safety record. Their facility is one of the most sophisticated in the United States.<br>
<br>
<br>
to learn more about the history of RRS, visit their website at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.rrs.org/History/body_history.html">www.rrs.org/History/body_history.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
